37
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:29,200
he still tried to catch Ji Bofeng in Qingchuan

38
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,560
to protect the people

39
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,960
and restore order.

40
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:33,959
I'm making a bold

41
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,560
request.

42
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,760
Please recover Li Bugui's soul

43
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,239
and let him go back to Qingchuan.

44
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,440
Well...

45
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,280
You can recover his soul?

46
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:46,920
Alas.

47
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,120
All of us know

48
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,120
