58
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,840
What's the point?

59
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,720
It's not him anyway.

60
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,920
Foolish girl,

61
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,640
His Majesty has agreed

62
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,840
to restore Li Bugui's soul

63
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,040
so Li Bugui may be alive.

64
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:37,320
It's a top secret. Tell nobody else.

65
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,359
Thank you, Your Majesty.

66
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,640
I'm willing to be your slave

67
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,480
forever.

68
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,640
Come on. Forget it.

69
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,760
