75
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,799
and send Yo back

76
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,799
to carry on their relationship.

77
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,120
Huh?

78
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,480
Yo,

79
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,800
I could tell

80
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,880
that you're in love

81
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,480
and don't want to stay here,

82
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,520
so why don't you go to have your life?

83
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,520
Destiny.

84
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,719
There was no such a precedent.

85
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,760
There was not a Spiritual Officer

86
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:38,159
who helped you to solve such a major case, either.

87
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,440
Fine.

88
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,160
Officer Meng Yo.

89
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,920
I can let you return to Qingchuan.

90
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,960
As for whether you can meet Li Bugui

91
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,400
and be with him,

92
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,320
it depends on your own destiny.

93
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,640
From now on,

94
00:04:58,640 --> 00:05:01,200
Meng Yo is removed from her post

95
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,280
and will be sent to Qingchuan

96
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,840
as a mortal.

97
