101
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,359
Town God Xie Lian.

102
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,280
Your Majesty.

103
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,520
I heard that you wanted to be transferred here long ago.

104
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:25,840
Since you have great credit in Meng Ge's case,

105
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:28,520
