106
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,720
I... I'm afraid that I'm incapable

107
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,840
of doing that.

108
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:37,840
So, I'd like to go back to my humble temple

109
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:38,960
