114
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,240
Ha-ha.

115
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,840
Yue is going back to face her fate,

116
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,920
I'd like to wait for her at my temple

117
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,520
because I can't

118
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,840
leave her alone.

119
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,880
Ha-ha.

120
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,560
Very well.

121
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,040
